    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for by a single owner. It looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership, with a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that still smells new. Every mechanical component is in perfect working order, and the car has a complete, up-to-date service history. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in absolute peak condition with zero compromises.",
